Numeric rows: 1 to 9
12 + (1..9) gives A..I
11 + (1..9) gives J..R
0 + (2..9) gives S..Z
Single numeric punch gives digits
Special combos used here:
12/5/8 gives {
11/5/8 gives }
0/5/8 gives _
Column-by-column decoding produced:
